WEBVTT

00:01.640 --> 00:03.740
Hello? Is there anyone out there?

00:03.750 --> 00:07.390
Hello? Hello? Can anyone hear me?

00:08.170 --> 00:11.280
Hello? My name is Joe Dubois.

00:12.060 --> 00:14.650
Is anyone receiving this message?

00:16.100 --> 00:19.100
I'm looking for Allison Dubois.

00:19.110 --> 00:22.150
If anybody's seen her,
this is her husband.

00:22.160 --> 00:26.610
Allison Dubois. Her
name is Allison Dubois.

00:34.230 --> 00:36.140
Still nothing?

00:36.840 --> 00:39.120
Oh,no,but that can mean
a lot of things,sweetie.

00:39.140 --> 00:44.040
Um,we know your mom is out there.
We just... we just got to sit tight.

00:45.260 --> 00:47.620
Dad...

00:48.110 --> 00:50.500
The food,it's all gone.

00:50.510 --> 00:52.850
Wait,how's that possible?

00:52.860 --> 00:54.970
I thought we still had
some energy bars left.

00:54.990 --> 00:58.600
Yeah,Bridgette and Marie
just split the last one.

01:02.960 --> 01:08.890
All right. Listen,Ariel, I'm going
to need you to watch your sisters.

01:09.560 --> 01:11.360
Well,wait,where are you going?

01:11.390 --> 01:13.320
I got to go outside,sweetie.

01:13.340 --> 01:15.620
I got to go find us some food.

01:16.370 --> 01:19.160
Wait,Dad! Please don't go!

01:19.170 --> 01:20.260
Sweetie,I'm not going far.

01:20.270 --> 01:22.410
I'm just going to check
the houses on our block.

01:22.430 --> 01:24.720
All right, they got to have
some food in there,all right.

01:24.730 --> 01:25.940
Please,Dad?

01:25.970 --> 01:29.810
Now you stay here, and watch the girls,

01:29.820 --> 01:32.730
make sure the house stays locked.

01:34.390 --> 01:37.920
No matter what, don't let anyone inside.

01:39.010 --> 01:40.880
Okay.

01:41.730 --> 01:43.990
Come here.

01:44.340 --> 01:45.820
I love you.

01:45.850 --> 01:47.690
I love you,Dad.

