- Earthquake!

02:26.420 --> 02:28.120
Come on, get the girls.

02:28.510 --> 02:29.340
Mom?

02:29.350 --> 02:32.710
- Ariel,get in the doorway!
- Get down!

02:34.960 --> 02:37.250
Quick,quick,quick,quick.

